      "content": "okay i see. so it sounds like it's a clash between the school wanting to promote inclusivity and parents wanting to control what their kids learn. i guess it's a hard balance to find. do you think there's a way they could actually work together on this, or is it just one of those things where one side has to win for the school to function properly?",
